<body>
  <!DOCTYPE html>
  <html>

  <head>
    <title>Affirmations</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>Affirmations</h1>
    <p>Below are some affirmations to help you start your day:</p>

    <ul class="appAffirmations">
      <li>I am worthy and deserving of love and happiness.</li>
      <li>I trust in my ability to handle any challenge that comes my way.</li>
      <li>I am surrounded by positivity and abundance.</li>
      <li>I release all negative thoughts and embrace positive thinking.</li>
      <li>I am confident and capable of achieving my goals.</li>
      <li>I am grateful for all the blessings in my life.</li>
      <li>I forgive myself and others, and let go of all grudges.</li>
      <li>I am proud of my accomplishments and excited for my future.</li>
      <li>I am healthy, strong, and full of vitality.</li>
      <li>I am at peace and in harmony with the universe.</li>
      <li>It is not my fault.</li>
    </ul>

    <form action="/wellness" method="POST">
      <h2>Write your own affirmation:</h2>
      <textarea name="affirmation" rows="5" cols="50"></textarea>
      <br>
      <button type="submit">Save</button>
    </form>
  </body>

  </html>


  <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>